Description_lang: Summons a Chaotic Essence which casts Chaotic Destruction, inflicting $372638s1 Cosmic damage to all players if successful.Upon interaction, the essence becomes hostile and instead continuously manifests Chaotic Motes. These motes channel $372636s1 Cosmic damage into targeted players every $372636T1 sec. for $372636D. When defeated each mote splits into additional motes.After $372634D the Chaotic Essence dissipates, granting all players $372639s1% increased damage done, $372639s2% increased healing done, and $372639s3% absorbs done for $372639D. This effect stacks for each Chaotic Mote slain.
